\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 Makes 6 servings\
\

\fs46 1/2 cup coarse grain Dijon mustard\
2 tablespoons Dijon mustard\
2 tablespoons Guinness stout\
1 tablespoon minced shallot\
1 teaspoon light brown sugar\
\
Combine all the ingredients in a mixing bowl & stir to combine.\'a0 Cover and refrigerate at least 2 hours.\'a0 This can be made up to 2 days in advance.
