\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 Makes 1 1/2 cups\
\

\fs44 1 cup sour cream\
6 tablespoons prepared white horseradish\
1 tablespoon finely chopped dill pickle\
1 tablespoon finely chopped fresh chives\
\
Whisk all the ingredients together in a mixing bowl.\'a0 Cover and refrigerate at least 2 hours.\'a0 This can be made up to 2 days in advance.\'a0\cell \lastrow\row
